  "proof_boundary": "Dry-run claim-audit and fixture scenario for issue #415. It documents the Codex-native packet shape required before LCO can materialize an advisory compaction-summary leaf with refs and omissions. It does not prove true Codex compaction-summary capture, model compaction, Codex source-store mutation, raw history access, live control, GUI mutation, external writes, unattended autonomy, npm publish, GitHub Release creation, or release readiness.",
  "next_action": "Keep public language on compaction observed until Codex exposes a sanitized CompactionCaptured or enriched PostCompact packet and an adapter validates the rejection rules."
